nd file path manipulation** - readFile, writeFile, fs operations with user input\n14. **Examine the sanitization utility** at `/repos/KamriHub/kamri-web/src/utils/sanitize.ts` carefully for bypass potential\n\n**CRITICAL:** For each finding, provide:\n- Exact file path and line number\n- The code snippet showing the sink\n- Whether user input can reach this sink (trace the data flow)\n- The render context (HTML body, attribute, JavaScript, CSS, URL)\n- Security risk assessment (HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW)\n\n**FOCUS ONLY ON NETWORK-ACCESSIBLE SINKS.** Exclude:\n- Build tools and scripts\n- Test files\n- Node modules\n- CLI utilities\n\nBe extremely thorough. Check every component file, every page, every API route.","max_turns":30},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}
